msgstr "[!java|c]void [/!]dragonReverse([!java|c]int [/!]ordre[!scala]:Int[/!], [!java|c]double [/!]x[!scala]:Double[/!], [!java|c]double [/!]y[!scala]:Double[/!], [!java|c]double [/!]z[!scala]:Double[/!], [!java|c]double [/!]t[!scala]:Double[/!])"

#. type: Content of: <p>
#: src/lessons/recursion/dragoncurve/DragonCurve2.html:34
